sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Domain as Domain Service
  participant Mongo as MongoDB Transaction
  participant Outbox
  participant Publisher as Kafka Publisher
  participant Kafka
  participant Consumers
  participant Projections
  Domain->>Mongo: Write state change
  Domain->>Outbox: Append event in same transaction
  Publisher->>Outbox: Poll unpublished event
  Publisher->>Kafka: Publish canonical event
  Kafka->>Consumers: Deliver event
  Consumers->>Consumers: Idempotency check
  Consumers->>Projections: Update read models
  Publisher->>Outbox: Mark published
